y_audit_2026-05-23.html:361:          <li>在模型初始化时加 warning, 让 <code>num_maskformer_stages</code> 截断行为可见</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/implementation_redundancy_audit_2026-05-23.html:410:    <p>当前最值得先做的优化是 P0 三项: cache 单次加载、prompt 分组预计算、明确 <code>num_maskformer_stages</code> 的实际语义。这三项不需要改变算法, 但会显著减少隐藏冗余和迁移语义漂移。</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:116:    <p class=\\\"meta\\\">生成时间：2026-05-23T12:00:52；入口配置：<code>Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml</code></p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:129:      <p>本次以 <code>Body-Tell/train.py::build_model()</code> 和 <code>phase1_voxtell_body.yaml</code> 实例化模型后统计，因此覆盖训练时真实使用的 Body-Tell 架构。当前模型没有冻结层，<strong>328.98M 参数全部参与 AdamW 优化</strong>。</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:137:        <div><span>encoder_channels</span><strong>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</strong></div>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:147:      <p class=\\\"note\\\">注意：配置请求 <code>num_maskformer_stages=5</code>，但代码使用 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code>，所以本次运行时实际 fused stage 数是 <code>4</code>，对应 <code>4</code> 个 mask projection 模块。</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:260:        <li>加载 YAML 配置：<code>Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml</code>。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:274:    &quot;config&quot;: &quot;Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml&quot;,\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:284:      &quot;encoder_channels&quot;: [\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:298:      &quot;num_maskformer_stages&quot;: 5,\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:320:    &quot;encoder_channels&quot;: [\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.html:335:    &quot;num_maskformer_stages&quot;: 5,\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:6:    \\\"config\\\": \\\"Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml\\\",\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:16:      \\\"encoder_channels\\\": [\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:30:      \\\"num_maskformer_stages\\\": 5,\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:52:    \\\"encoder_channels\\\": [\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/body_tell_parameter_audit.json:67:    \\\"num_maskformer_stages\\\": 5,\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:121:      <p><strong>Body-Tell 的 encoder 确实是轻量版</strong>：它不是 nnU-Net 风格的 <code>ResidualEncoder</code>，而是 5 个普通 3D 卷积块组成的 <code>_BodyEncoder</code>。与 VoxTell 的 6-stage residual backbone 相比，encoder 参数少约 <strong>81.80M</strong>，单看 encoder 是非常明显的差别。</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:123:      <p><strong>如果当前训练表现为模型难以学到稳定的空间/器官结构，encoder 成为瓶颈是一个高优先级假设。</strong>Body-Tell 的 decoder 和 prompt 模块很重，但 visual backbone 只有浅层非残差 CNN；这会让文本侧容量远大于视觉侧容量，模型可能缺少足够强的 occupancy-to-anatomy 表征。</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:134:            <td><code>Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml:3-16</code></td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:135:            <td><code>encoder_channels=[32,64,128,256,320]</code>，<code>decoder_layer=-1</code>，<code>num_maskformer_stages=5</code>，<code>num_heads=32</code>。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:160:            <td>使用 <code>dynamic_network_architectures</code> 的 <code>ResidualEncoder</code>，<code>return_skips=True</code>，<code>disable_default_stem=False</code>。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:165:            <td>从 <code>plans.json</code> 读取 architecture kwargs，并设置 <code>decoder_layer=4</code>、<code>text_embedding_dim=2560</code>、<code>query_dim=2048</code>。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:174:            <td><code>/home/comp/csrkzhu/miniconda3/lib/python3.13/site-packages/dynamic_network_architectures/building_blocks/residual_encoders.py:13</code></td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:179:            <td><code>/home/comp/csrkzhu/miniconda3/lib/python3.13/site-packages/dynamic_network_architectures/building_blocks/residual.py:13</code></td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:188:      <p><strong>本次已经从三层证据交叉确定 VoxTell 的 nnU-Net-style encoder 结构</strong>：VoxTell v1.1 <code>plans.json</code>、VoxTell model 构造代码、以及当前环境安装的 <code>dynamic_network_architectures</code> 源码。结论是：VoxTell 使用的不是一个普通 CNN encoder，而是 <code>ResidualEncoder</code> 包装的 6-stage residual feature pyramid。</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:204:            <td>第一个 residual block 使用 stage 的 <code>initial_stride</code>；同一 stage 内后续 block 都是 stride=1。<code>n_blocks_per_stage</code> 决定每个 stage 的深度。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:250:            <td>occupancy 没有 HU/intensity texture、跨模态强度差异和图像噪声模式；图像 backbone 需要更强的纹理和尺度建模能力。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:278:            <td>decoder 只接收 <code>encoder_channels</code>，与 nnU-Net encoder 解耦。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:284:            <td>配置请求 5，但代码用 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code>，实际只有 4 个 projection。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:322:      <p class=\\\"note\\\">统计方法：本地实例化 <code>VoxTellBodyModel(VoxTellBodyConfig())</code>；VoxTell 使用 v1.1 <code>plans.json</code> 的 architecture kwargs，并按推理入口设置 <code>decoder_layer=4</code>、<code>text_embedding_dim=2560</code>、<code>query_dim=2048</code>、<code>num_heads=32</code>、<code>deep_supervision=False</code>。由于当前环境缺少 <code>positional_encodings</code> 包，统计 VoxTell 参数时仅 stub 了固定 positional buffer；该 buffer 不是 trainable parameter，不影响上述参数量。</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:365:        <li><strong>第二优先级：引入 plans-like ResidualEncoder，但仍保持 5 stages。</strong>可以使用 <code>dynamic_network_architectures</code> 的 <code>ResidualEncoder</code> 或本地复刻 <code>BasicBlockD</code> 思路；输入仍是 occupancy，norm/activation 可先保持 Body-Tell 的 <code>GroupNorm + GELU</code>，避免一次改变过多变量。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-23/done/bodytell_encoder_backbone_report_2026-05-23.html:368:        <li><strong>修正或确认 mask stage 语义。</strong>当前配置写 <code>num_maskformer_stages=5</code>，但实际 <code>fused_stage_count=4</code>。如果 encoder 改成 6-stage，这个问题会直接影响多尺度融合是否对齐 VoxTell。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_standalone_dependency_audit_2026-05-23.html:172:Body-Tell/train.py:34 from body_tell.models.voxtell_body_model import VoxTellBodyConfig, VoxTellBodyModel</pre>\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_standalone_dependency_audit_2026-05-23.html:229:            <td>复制或新建 <code>Body-Tell/slurm/phase1.sh</code>，从脚本自身定位项目根目录，并执行 <code>torchrun train.py --config configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml</code>。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_standalone_dependency_audit_2026-05-23.html:233:            <td><code>Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml:17-18</code>, <code>Body-Tell/train.py:3-9</code></td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_standalone_dependency_audit_2026-05-23.html:350:            <td>读取 <code>configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml</code> 后检查 <code>data.root</code> 派生路径。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_standalone_dependency_audit_2026-05-23.html:362:        <li>把推荐启动命令改成项目内命令：<code>cd Body-Tell &amp;&amp; torchrun --nproc_per_node=2 train.py --config configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml --checkpoint-dir checkpoints/phase1_bz2</code>。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_migration_potential_bugs_2026-05-23.html:223:            <td><code>Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml:18</code> 是 <code>root: Body-Tell</code>；<code>train.py:5-9</code> 的说明却是从 <code>Body-Tell/</code> 内运行 <code>python train.py --config configs/...</code>。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_migration_potential_bugs_2026-05-23.html:240:            <td>即使迁出后修了 <code>configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml</code>，旧 checkpoint 仍可能把 <code>data.root: Body-Tell</code> 带回推理流程。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_migration_potential_bugs_2026-05-23.html:419:  --config configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml \\\\\\nBody-Tell/reports/potential-bug/body_tell_migration_potential_bugs_2026-05-23.html:424:  --config configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml \\\\\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_sampling_vocabulary_optimization_report.html:176:        <td><code>phase1_voxtell_body.yaml</code> 指向 <code>S2I-Dataset-70cls/data</code>、<code>class_presence.json</code>、<code>dataset_split.json</code>，默认 <code>num_positive: 2</code>、<code>num_negative: 1</code>。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:218:            <td>Encoder backbone</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:220:            <td>当前 encoder 无法复用 VoxTell encoder 权重，也很可能限制性能上限。这个差异不是“轻量配置”，而是 backbone 类型不同。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:225:            <td><span class=\\\"tag bad\\\">真实存在</span> 两层根因：(1) Body-Tell 配置写 5，但运行时被 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code> 截成 4 级；(2) Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）vs VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell_model.py:74</code>）。两者乘积决定实际 projection 输出。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:238:            <td>Body-Tell 当前 <code>volume_size=[129,108,256]</code>（见 <code>configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml:25</code>，2026-05-24 commit <code>5c31e57</code> 后裁剪到此尺寸）不是 192³，直接加载 VoxTell <code>pos_embed</code> 会遇到 shape/语义问题。需要明确动态重建或改成 192³ profile。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:256:            <td>使用 <code>dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.residual_encoders.ResidualEncoder</code>，参数与 VoxTell v1.1 plan 一致。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:315:        <li>新增配置文件 <code>Body-Tell/configs/phase1_voxtell_aligned.yaml</code>，设置 <code>encoder_channels: [32,64,128,256,320,320]</code>、<code>n_blocks_per_stage: [1,3,4,6,6,6]</code>、<code>decoder_layer: 4</code>、<code>num_maskformer_stages: 5</code>。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:316:        <li>在模型配置中加入 <code>architecture: voxtell_v1_1</code> 或 <code>backbone: residual_encoder</code>，让旧轻量模型和 aligned 模型可并存。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:318:        <li>把依赖写入 Body-Tell 环境声明：<code>dynamic-network-architectures&gt;=0.4.1,&lt;0.5</code> 和 <code>einops</code>。若采用 VoxTell 原始位置编码实现，再加入 <code>positional-encodings</code>。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:342:        <li>encoder 变为 6-stage 后，projection stage 自然恢复为 5 级，不再用 <code>len(encoder_channels)-1</code> 隐式截断配置。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:376:        <li>不要把旧 Body-Tell checkpoint 与 aligned 模型静默混用。旧 checkpoint 应只用于旧架构；aligned checkpoint 应带 <code>architecture: voxtell_v1_1</code>。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:466:            <td>checkpoint 中记录 <code>architecture</code>；inference strict 校验；不给旧 checkpoint 自动迁移到 aligned 结构。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:482:        <li><strong>随后做 P2/P3 encoder 和 decoder。</strong> 当前 encoder 参数差距过大且结构不同，性能问题很可能与此相关；若目标是对齐 VoxTell，不应继续保留轻量自定义 backbone 作为主路线。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:484:        <li><strong>最后才跑完整训练实验。</strong> 没有 architecture/weight audit 通过前，不建议直接用 VoxTell checkpoint warm-start 长训。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_training_loop_eval_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:291:      <li>模型字段应引用 SP-A aligned 架构：<code>architecture: voxtell_v1_1</code>、<code>num_maskformer_stages: 5</code>。在 SP-A 未完成前，该 profile 可以存在但不作为默认训练入口。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_training_loop_eval_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:327:        <li><code>train.py:464-473</code> 当前 checkpoint 只写 <code>{epoch, model_state_dict, optimizer_state_dict, metrics, config}</code>；<strong>不包含</strong> scheduler state（因为根本没有 scheduler）、<strong>不包含</strong> AMP scaler state（虽然 <code>train.py:25, 361, 444</code> 已使用 <code>GradScaler</code>，但 scaler.state_dict() 未持久化）、<strong>不包含</strong> <code>global_step</code> / <code>iteration_in_epoch</code> / <code>architecture</code> tag。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_training_loop_eval_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:332:      <li>checkpoint 写入 <code>model_state_dict</code>、<code>optimizer_state_dict</code>、<code>scheduler_state_dict</code>、<code>epoch</code>、<code>iteration_in_epoch</code>、<code>global_step</code>、<code>total_updates</code>、<strong><code>scaler.state_dict()</code>（新增，对应已存在但未持久化的 <code>GradScaler</code>）</strong>、配置 hash、<code>architecture</code> 字段。</li>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:349:          <td>5 scales vs 实际 4 scales（被 <code>min(5, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code> 截断）。</td>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:440:<p><strong>Owner:</strong> sp_a_architecture_worker</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:448:<p><strong>Owner:</strong> sp_a_architecture_worker</p>\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/PROMPT.md:1:You are sp_a_architecture_worker.\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:9:{\\\"type\\\":\\\"item.completed\\\",\\\"item\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"item_1\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"command_execution\\\",\\\"command\\\":\\\"/bin/bash -lc \\\\\\\"sed -n '1,260p' Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\\\\\\\"\\\",\\\"aggregated_output\\\":\\\"<!doctype html>\\\\n<html lang=\\\\\\\"zh-CN\\\\\\\">\\\\n<head>\\\\n  <meta charset=\\\\\\\"utf-8\\\\\\\">\\\\n  <meta name=\\\\\\\"viewport\\\\\\\" content=\\\\\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\\\\\\\">\\\\n  <title>Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</title>\\\\n  <style>\\\\n    :root {\\\\n      --ink: #17202a;\\\\n      --muted: #5d6875;\\\\n      --line: #d8e0e7;\\\\n      --panel: #f6f8fa;\\\\n      --soft: #eef4f7;\\\\n      --accent: #14677b;\\\\n      --warn: #9a4a17;\\\\n      --bad: #993333;\\\\n      --good: #276749;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\\\\n\\\\n    body {\\\\n      margin: 0;\\\\n      color: var(--ink);\\\\n      background: #ffffff;\\\\n      font: 15px/1.62 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\\\\\"Segoe UI\\\\\\\", sans-serif;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    header {\\\\n      padding: 34px 42px 24px;\\\\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\\\\n      background: #f8fbfd;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    main {\\\\n      max-width: 1220px;\\\\n      padding: 28px 42px 56px;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    h1 {\\\\n      margin: 0 0 8px;\\\\n      font-size: 30px;\\\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    h2 {\\\\n      margin: 30px 0 12px;\\\\n      font-size: 22px;\\\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    h3 {\\\\n      margin: 20px 0 8px;\\\\n      font-size: 17px;\\\\n      letter-spacing: 0;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    p { margin: 8px 0; }\\\\n\\\\n    code {\\\\n      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;\\\\n      background: #edf3f7;\\\\n      border-radius: 4px;\\\\n      padding: 1px 4px;\\\\n      font-size: 0.92em;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    pre {\\\\n      overflow-x: auto;\\\\n      background: #111827;\\\\n      color: #f7fafc;\\\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\\\n      padding: 14px 16px;\\\\n      font-size: 13px;\\\\n      line-height: 1.5;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    pre code {\\\\n      background: transparent;\\\\n      padding: 0;\\\\n      color: inherit;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    table {\\\\n      width: 100%;\\\\n      border-collapse: collapse;\\\\n      margin: 12px 0 22px;\\\\n      font-size: 14px;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    th, td {\\\\n      padding: 9px 10px;\\\\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\\\\n      vertical-align: top;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    th {\\\\n      text-align: left;\\\\n      background: #f1f5f8;\\\\n      color: #24313d;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    ul, ol { padding-left: 22px; }\\\\n    li { margin: 5px 0; }\\\\n\\\\n    .meta { color: var(--muted); }\\\\n    .num {\\\\n      text-align: right;\\\\n      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\\\\n      white-space: nowrap;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .cards {\\\\n      display: grid;\\\\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(190px, 1fr));\\\\n      gap: 12px;\\\\n      margin: 16px 0;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .card {\\\\n      border: 1px solid var(--line);\\\\n      border-radius: 8px;\\\\n      background: var(--panel);\\\\n      padding: 14px 16px;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .card span {\\\\n      display: block;\\\\n      color: var(--muted);\\\\n      font-size: 13px;\\\\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .card strong {\\\\n      color: var(--accent);\\\\n      display: block;\\\\n      font-size: 22px;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .callout {\\\\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);\\\\n      background: var(--soft);\\\\n      padding: 12px 14px;\\\\n      margin: 12px 0 18px;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .warnbox {\\\\n      border-left-color: var(--warn);\\\\n      background: #fff7ed;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .badbox {\\\\n      border-left-color: var(--bad);\\\\n      background: #fff5f5;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .tag {\\\\n      display: inline-block;\\\\n      border-radius: 999px;\\\\n      padding: 1px 8px;\\\\n      font-size: 12px;\\\\n      font-weight: 650;\\\\n      white-space: nowrap;\\\\n    }\\\\n\\\\n    .ok { color: var(--good); background: #eaf7ef; }\\\\n    .warn { color: var(--warn); background: #fff2df; }\\\\n    .bad { color: var(--bad); background: #ffe7e7; }\\\\n    .info { color: var(--accent); background: #e7f3f7; }\\\\n\\\\n    @media (max-width: 860px) {\\\\n      header, main {\\\\n        padding-left: 20px;\\\\n        padding-right: 20px;\\\\n      }\\\\n      table {\\\\n        display: block;\\\\n        overflow-x: auto;\\\\n        white-space: nowrap;\\\\n      }\\\\n    }\\\\n  </style>\\\\n</head>\\\\n<body>\\\\n  <header>\\\\n    <h1>Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</h1>\\\\n    <p class=\\\\\\\"meta\\\\\\\">日期：2026-05-24；目标：让 Body-Tell 在结构和权重语义上尽量对齐 VoxTell v1.1，优先支持 VoxTell checkpoint 复用，而不是只做到 tensor shape 能加载。</p>\\\\n  </header>\\\\n\\\\n  <main>\\\\n    <section>\\\\n      <h2>核验结论</h2>\\\\n      <div class=\\\\\\\"callout\\\\\\\">\\\\n        <p><strong>原差异报告中的核心不一致真实存在。</strong> 其中最影响 VoxTell 权重复用的是两类问题：一类是参数量和模块拓扑明显不同，例如 encoder/decoder；另一类是参数 shape 一致但 forward 语义不同，例如 transformer decoder。</p>\\\\n      </div>\\\\n\\\\n      <div class=\\\\\\\"cards\\\\\\\">\\\\n        <div class=\\\\\\\"card\\\\\\\"><span>Body-Tell 当前参数</span><strong>328.98M</strong></div>\\\\n        <div class=\\\\\\\"card\\\\\\\"><span>VoxTell v1.1 参数</span><strong>440.03M</strong></div>\\\\n        <div class=\\\\\\\"card\\\\\\\"><span>Body encoder</span><strong>8.49M</strong></div>\\\\n        <div class=\\\\\\\"card\\\\\\\"><span>VoxTell encoder</span><strong>90.30M</strong></div>\\\\n        <div class=\\\\\\\"card\\\\\\\"><span>Transformer 参数</span><strong>251.86M</strong></div>\\\\n        <div class=\\\\\\\"card\\\\\\\"><span>最高风险</span><strong>shape 同而语义不同</strong></div>\\\\n      </div>\\\\n\\\\n      <table>\\\\n        <thead>\\\\n          <tr><th>差异点</th><th>核验结果</th><th>对权重复用的影响</th><th>证据位置</th></tr>\\\\n        </thead>\\\\n        <tbody>\\\\n          <tr>\\\\n            <td>Transformer decoder</td>\\\\n            <td><span class=\\\\\\\"tag bad\\\\\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 使用 <code>activation=\\\\\\\"gelu\\\\\\\"</code>，pre-norm path 执行 self-attention；VoxTell 默认 <code>relu</code>，active <code>forward_pre</code> 跳过 self-attention，只做 cross-attention 和 FFN。</td>\\\\n            <td>参数名和 shape 可 100% 对上，但加载 VoxTell 权重后语义不等价。小模型同权重实验输出最大绝对差为 <code>0.9258</code>。</td>\\\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:69</code>、<code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:137</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:224</code></td>\\\\n          </tr>\\\\n          <tr>\\\\n            <td>Encoder backbone</td>\\\\n            <td><span class=\\\\\\\"tag bad\\\\\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 5-stage 手写 ConvBlock；VoxTell 是 6-stage <code>ResidualEncoder</code>，features 为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320,320]</code>，blocks 为 <code>[1,3,4,6,6,6]</code>。</td>\\\\n            <td>当前 encoder 无法复用 VoxTell encoder 权重，也很可能限制性能上限。这个差异不是“轻量配置”，而是 backbone 类型不同。</td>\\\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:155</code>、<code>VoxTell/models-weight/voxtell/voxtell_v1.1/plans.json:20</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:131</code></td>\\\\n          </tr>\\\\n          <tr>\\\\n            <td>Mask projections（含 <code>num_heads</code>）</td>\\\\n            <td><span class=\\\\\\\"tag bad\\\\\\\">真实存在</span> 两层根因：(1) Body-Tell 配置写 5，但运行时被 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code> 截成 4 级；(2) Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）vs VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell_model.py:74</code>）。两者乘积决定实际 projection 输出。</td>\\\\n            <td>Body-Tell 实际输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>（<code>channels × 32</code>，stage 0 例外）；VoxTell 实际输出 <strong><code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级</strong>（<code>channels × 1</code>）。<strong>原报告写 VoxTell 最高级 <code>10240</code> 是错误的。</strong> 即使 encoder 升到 6 级、stage 截断消除，<code>num_heads</code> 不同会导致 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与下游 mask fusion 模块的 shape 不匹配，权重无法直接复用。</td>\\\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>、<code>:83</code>、<code>:89</code>；<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:74</code>、<code>:177</code>、<code>:370</code></td>\\\\n          </tr>\\\\n          <tr>\\\\n            <td>Decoder</td>\\\\n            <td><span class=\\\\\\\"tag bad\\\\\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 4-stage 手写 decoder，<code>GroupNorm + GELU</code>；VoxTell 是 5-stage <code>VoxTellDecoder</code>，使用 <code>StackedConvBlocks</code> 并继承 encoder 的 <code>InstanceNorm3d + LeakyReLU + conv_bias=true</code>。</td>\\\\n            <td>当前 decoder 无法复用 VoxTell decoder 权重。VoxTell 还总是构造 <code>seg_layers</code>，用于 checkpoint 兼容。</td>\\\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:174</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:280</code></td>\\\\n          </tr>\\\\n          <tr>\\\\n            <td>Position / memory 排列</td>\\\\n            <td><span class=\\\\\\\"tag warn\\\\\\\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 动态生成 <code>D,H,W</code> 顺序的位置编码；VoxTell 使用 init 时固定的 <code>pos_embed</code> buffer，并用 <code>H,W,D</code> 顺序 flatten。</td>\\\\n            <td>Body-Tell 当前 <code>volume_size=[129,108,256]</code>（见 <code>configs/phase1_voxtell_body.yaml:25</code>，2026-05-24 commit <code>5c31e57</code> 后裁剪到此尺寸）不是 192³，直接加载 VoxTell <code>pos_embed</code> 会遇到 shape/语义问题。需要明确动态重建或改成 192³ profile。</td>\\\\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:118</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:185</code>、<code>:229</code></td>\\\\n          </tr>\\\\n        </tbody>\\\\n      </table>\\\\n    </section>\\\\n\\\\n    <section>\\\\n      <h2>目标状态</h2>\\\\n      <p>新增一个 VoxTell-aligned 架构路径，而不是在现有轻量模型上做零散补丁。该路径的 state dict 命名应尽量贴近 VoxTell，降低权重加载映射复杂度。</p>\\\\n\\\\n      <table>\\\\n        <thead>\\\\n          <tr><th>模块</th><th>目标实现</th><th>权重复用要求</th></tr>\\\\n        </thead>\\\\n        <tbody>\\\\n          <tr>\\\\n            <td><code>encoder</code></td>\\\\n            <td>使用 <code>dynamic_network_architectures.building_blocks.residual_encoders.ResidualEncoder</code>，参数与 VoxTell v1.1 plan 一致。</td>\\\\n            <td>加载 VoxTell <code>encoder.*</code> 权重，shape mismatch 必须报错。</td>\\\\n          </tr>\\\\n          <tr>\\\\n            <td><code>decoder</code></td>\\\\n\\\",\\\"exit_code\\\":0,\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\"}}\\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/events.jsonl:11:{\\\"type\\\":\\\"item.completed\\\",\\\"item\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"item_3\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"command_execution\\\",\\\"command\\\":\\\"/bin/bash -lc \\\\\\\"find Body-Tell -maxdepth 4 -type f | sort | sed -n '1,220p'\\\\\\\"\\\",\\\"aggregated_output\\\":\\\"Body-Tell/artifacts/text_embeddings/prompt_embeddings.pt\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/dataset.py\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__init__.py\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/dataset.cpython-312.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/dataset.cpython-313.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/__init__.cpython-312.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/__init__.cpython-313.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/vocabulary.cpython-312.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/__pycache__/vocabulary.cpython-313.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/data/vocabulary.py\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/__init__.py\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/losses/__init__.py\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/losses/prompt_losses.py\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/losses/__pycache__/__init__.cpython-312.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/losses/__pycache__/__init__.cpython-313.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/losses/__pycache__/prompt_losses.cpython-312.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/losses/__pycache__/prompt_losses.cpython-313.pyc\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/metrics/__init__.py\\\\nBody-Tell/body_tell/metrics/prompt_metrics.py\\\\n