ignment.html</code></td><td>Generated HTML audit report with machine-readable payload.</td></tr>\\\\\\\\n        <tr><td><code>Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/RESULT.html</code></td><td>This result report.</td></tr>\\\\\\\\n      </tbody>\\\\\\\\n    </table>\\\\\\\\n    <p class=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"meta\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\">Pre-existing worktree state included a modified <code>Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/workflow_manifest.yaml</code> and existing files under this run directory. They were not edited as part of this task.</p>\\\\\\\\n  </section>\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n  <section>\\\\\\\\n    <h2>Verification</h2>\\\\\\\\n    <table>\\\\\\\\n      <thead><tr><th>Command</th><th>Result / important output</th></tr></thead>\\\\\\\\n      <tbody>\\\\\\\\n        <tr>\\\\\\\\n          <td><code>conda run -n voxtell python Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py --help</code></td>\\\\\\\\n          <td>Exit 0. Help lists <code>--config</code>, <code>--voxtell-dir</code>, <code>--pos-embed-policy</code>, <code>--skip-checkpoint</code>, <code>--skip-state-dict-compare</code>, and <code>--html-output</code>.</td>\\\\\\\\n        </tr>\\\\\\\\n        <tr>\\\\\\\\n          <td><code>conda run -n voxtell python -m py_compile Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py Body-Tell/tests/test_voxtell_transformer_compat.py</code></td>\\\\\\\\n          <td>Exit 0.</td>\\\\\\\\n        </tr>\\\\\\\\n        <tr>\\\\\\\\n          <td><code>conda run -n voxtell python Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py --html-output Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/audit_voxtell_alignment.html</code></td>\\\\\\\\n          <td>\\\\\\\\n            Exit 0. Key output:\\\\\\\\n            <pre>Body-Tell current: num_heads=32, projection outputs [32, 2048, 4096, 8192]\\\\\\\\nVoxTell source default: num_heads=1, projection outputs [32, 64, 128, 256, 320]\\\\\\\\nVoxTell v1.1 predictor/checkpoint: num_heads=32, projection outputs [32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]\\\\\\\\ncheckpoint pos_embed 